{"tid":2179656,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中學改設蹲廁迎內地客 深紅校長入考評局  團體憂敏感試題消失","createTime":"2020-08-29T09:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T11:32:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cede36c414eed31bcdb4d31c2abeca32499bd228","tid":2179656,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:29:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/OTTZGBJSWVFPFDXYZM4UYRCRHM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FOTTZGBJSWVFPFDXYZM4UYRCRHM%2F&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5Zg6WLWD%2BvnO7xCw116w%2BR6c%3D&h=0d1a4994\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FOTTZGBJSWVFPFDXYZM4UYRCRHM%2F&h=93ba68b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/OTTZGBJSWVFPFDXYZM4UYRCRHM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中學改設蹲廁迎內地客 深紅校長入考評局 <br />\n團體憂敏感試題消失<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_11XvFrDCXuVd8SyqQY80lTQTjg=/4252x2412/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PSKIB2OFDREMNERNZNGBNPHGHI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_11XvFrDCXuVd8SyqQY80lTQTjg%3D%2F4252x2412%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPSKIB2OFDREMNERNZNGBNPHGHI.gif&h=e61e53bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】經歷過文憑試歷史科試題風波的考評局，繼早前有多個評核發展部經理辭職後，再出現人事變動。政府昨日宣佈，委任元朗西門英才中學校長簡加言，以及中史科教師陳嘉雯加入考評局委員會。簡曾多次公開批評近年的社會運動，又與內地學校狂搞交流活動，甚至將校內坐廁改成蹲廁以配合到訪的大陸人，被形容為「深紅校長」。<br />\n<br />\n政府昨日公佈最新考評局委員會成員名單，小學校長梁翠珍、嶺大校董會成。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n考評局委員會是局方最高決策單位，負責。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kHEvPtsGrBWLc9iRSaQYcuee1Nk=/640x397/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4XYZNA6T5JFFNGEN6KTHTWVFCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkHEvPtsGrBWLc9iRSaQYcuee1Nk%3D%2F640x397%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4XYZNA6T5JFFNGEN6KTHTWVFCA.jpg&h=183e6d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■簡加言在2016至2018年內舉行了三十次內地交流團，令教師疲於奔命。西門英才中學網頁圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩年辦30次內地交流團<br />\n<br />\n簡加言是著名的「深紅校長」，曾多次接受中共官媒訪問，批評「佔中」、。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n元朗西門英才中學在簡加言治下頻繁與內地中學進行互訪，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳嘉雯是天主教母佑會蕭明中學協作副校長兼中史科教師，曾自創多個。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n教育倡議團體「教育野」發言人、前香港眾志成員鄭家朗表示，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a1edf00c2d166b20712aa0a76c00e6dd755d881c","tid":2179656,"uid":238370,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:42:03.000Z","msg":"坐廁改蹲廁on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3877255e39ee5c1dd14aafb61351070957b00e","tid":2179656,"uid":44209,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:45:58.000Z","msg":"陳嘉雯，做得天主教學校副校長，應該都係信徒，你點對得住支那比人拆十字架教堂嘅弟兄姊妹？"},{"pid":"716a180eda479a2d85147dbeec43dd9bad72f9dc","tid":2179656,"uid":44209,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a1edf00c2d166b20712aa0a76c00e6dd755d881c","tid":2179656,"uid":238370,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:42:03.000Z","msg":"坐廁改蹲廁on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:46:44.000Z","msg":"蹲廁真係最撚on9嘅發明，完全唔會用"},{"pid":"f4681c8684a3ae0deda6a04f4c04cfce4a5ca8f8","tid":2179656,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:47:26.000Z","msg":"係度講有咩用<br />\n佢地繼續unun腳袋十幾萬人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c845c8f4c004fe4fdc4b2b63138e2ae0cc974047","tid":2179656,"uid":360777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T10:16:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/hongkong/text/2020/0605/459077.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fhongkong%2Ftext%2F2020%2F0605%2F459077.html&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5Zg6WLWD%2BvnO7xCw116w%2BR6c%3D&h=28592b0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/hongkong/text/2020/0605/459077.html</a> <br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">憂蹲廁播毒 教育局：26間學校申請換廁</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 小四至中二將在下周一（8日）復課，沙田瀝源邨祿泉樓出現新冠肺炎小型爆發，令附近多校嚴陣以待；雖然口罩及防疫物資供應不再緊張，但若學校內仍然使用蹲廁或有傳播風險。教育局指，疫情以來共接獲26間資助學校申請緊急更換學校的蹲廁成座廁。當中約三成（8間）學校能趕及在下周一（8日）復課前完成。<br />\n<br />\n  有小學校內沿用蹲廁約15年，由於擔心沒廁板的蹲廁容易傳播疾病，校方今年二月自行花費約20萬，以及申請教育局的緊急工程換走校內蹲廁，料可在下周一復課前，將蹲廁換成座廁。<br />\n<br />\n  按教育局現行建校安排，學校洗手間會安裝座廁，但個別學校會因學生需要，將部分座廁轉為蹲廁，以方便清潔。"},{"pid":"6cf09206ba8c5b343dd43cfb053e62b73d2602ce","tid":2179656,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T10:35:12.000Z","msg":"呢隻人種真係完全冇得救"},{"pid":"f4b4576f84c7afef1d230295ff651d8b611f385a","tid":2179656,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T10:36:40.000Z","msg":"屌你不如係後門種兩塊草地比支那豬黎屙仲迎合啦"},{"pid":"7d8812e89b80d655c3a05e1fd447f07e08b021f0","tid":2179656,"uid":54579,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"716a180eda479a2d85147dbeec43dd9bad72f9dc","tid":2179656,"uid":44209,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a1edf00c2d166b20712aa0a76c00e6dd755d881c","tid":2179656,"uid":238370,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:42:03.000Z","msg":"坐廁改蹲廁on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:46:44.000Z","msg":"蹲廁真係最撚on9嘅發明，完全唔會用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T10:51:07.000Z","msg":"好似狗先會用"},{"pid":"84f70b77138efce5a163994030ae0316cbe822e7","tid":2179656,"uid":38757,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T10:54:49.000Z","msg":"佢學校校長廁所係咪都係踎廁？"},{"pid":"68cf3ee35b95770789